FBIS3-33242 "drlat035_o_94007" FBIS-LAT-94-035 Document Type:Daily Report 22 Feb 1994 Colombia De Greiff Rules Out Immediate Surrender PA2002030294 Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 1 in Spanish 0130 GMT 20 Feb 94 PA2002030294 Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 1 Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [From the "TV Today" newscast] [Text] Prosecutor General Gustavo de Greiff said today that the country should not have any illusions over the imminent surrender of Cali Cartel drug traffickers, but added that in less than a month they will have probably turned themselves in. He also reiterated that there are no legal cases pending in Colombia against Pacho Herrera [not further identified], but that investigations shall continue.
